NAME
    Protocol::EMIUCP - Library for EMI-UCP protocol

SYNOPSIS
      use Protocol::EMIUCP;
      my $msg = Protocol::EMIUCP->new_message(
          o => 1, ot => 51, adc => 507998000, oadc => 6638,
          mt => 3, amsg_utf8 => 'TEST',
      );
      print $msg->as_string;

DESCRIPTION
    This is a library for EMI-UCP protocol which is primarily used to
    connect to short message service centers (SMSCs) for mobile telephones.

    The library provides an API for handling EMI-UCP messages and
    connections as client or server.

    The Protocol::EMIUCP package joins a few more pacakges in one factory
    class.

SEE ALSO
    Protocol::EMIUCP::Message, http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/EMI_(protocol)

BUGS
    If you find the bug or want to implement new features, please report it
    at https://github.com/dex4er/perl-Protocol-EMIUCP/issues

    The code repository is available at
    http://github.com/dex4er/perl-Protocol-EMIUCP

